A Ferrari drives in at Edwin Sodi's Blackhead Consulting HQ. JOHANNESBURG - Politically connected businessman, Edwin Sodi has had his luxury sportscars seized. The National Prosecuting Authority’s Asset Forfeiture Unit swooped in on the vehicles owned by Sodi and his company Blackhead Consulting. READ: Businessman Edwin Sodi's luxury cars seized They include a Ferrari, valued at around R3-million and a Bentley Continental valued at more than R3-million. eNCA reporter, Aviwe Mtila was in Bryanston when it happened and shares more details in the video below. Politically connected businessman Edwin Sodi has had his luxury sportscars seized. eNCA's Aviwe Mtila reports. Courtesy #DStv403